Seriously enjoyed this.  In fact I took all the curanderismo classes.  I think this is not just traditional medicine but the wave of the future.  This will become incorporated into our "modern" medicine and they will augment each other and greatly improve medical care.

Professor Torres is enthusiastic in his presentation of the course materials. The guest speaker are what we would have to call experts in their fields. The demonstrations are clear and well explained. I can't say enough good things about the course and its presenters.

Finishing this course in 2 days was nothing short of the amazing content and information that was provided. I am interested in more classes such as this and I'd like to thank Professor Cheo for hosting this course and bringing insight into our culture!
